Download TIGER shapes for Primary Roads

Source: R/primary_roads.R
tt_primary_roads.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Primary Roads

Usage

tt_primary_roads(year = 2024)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. 2000 and 2010-2024 are currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

 # takes > 5 seconds
# Wrapped in try due to false positive 304 errors
try(tt_primary_roads()) # downloads slow on CRAN
